OL,7,FA woman applying makeup and a man
OL,8,Fsteering with his knees as he ate fast
OL,9,Ffood are two of the offences captured
OL,10,Fby police patrolling motorways in a
OL,11,Fspecially adapted lorry cab.
OL,13,FPolice recorded 63 offences over two
OL,14,Fdays of an operation to tackle
OL,15,Fdangerous driving on the M6, M40 and
OL,16,FA46 in
OL,18,FOperation Tramline was carried out on
OL,19,FMonday 29 April and Thursday 3 May
OL,20,F2024, with police observing drivers
OL,21,Ffrom a National Highways supercab.
