OL,9,FPolice say the elevated position of
OL,10,Fthe supercab allows officers to
OL,11,Fcapture footage of some of the most
OL,12,Fdangerous driving offences possible
OL,13,Fknown as the 'Fatal 4' - including not
OL,14,Fwearing a seatbelt and using a
OL,15,Fhandheld mobile phone whilst driving.
OL,17,FOnce an offence is identified, an
OL,18,Funmarked police car intercepts the
OL,19,Foffending driver.
