OL,7,FSergeant Scott Good, Warwickshire
OL,8,FPolice said: "Most drivers who use our
OL,9,Froads every day are safe and sensible
OL,10,Fbehind the wheel, but there are some
OL,11,Fwho are putting themselves and others
OL,12,Fat risk by simply ignoring the law.
OL,13,FThat's where Operation Tramline is
OL,14,Finvaluable in helping to change driver
OL,15,Fbehaviours and encourage compliance
OL,16,Fwith driving laws.
